Usage: setGenerateViaMode [-help] [-reset] [-auto {true|false}]
                          [-ndr_only {true|false}]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-reset                         # Resets all or specified options to default value
-auto {true|false}             # enable auto via generation when design is
                               # loaded (bool, default=false)
-ndr_only {true|false}         # generate vias for non default rules only
                               # (bool, default=false)